Package: sqlservr
Type: Package
Title: An Easy and Fast Interface to SQL Server
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Gurcke", email = "simon@gurcke.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a function to quickly write large amounts of data to a SQL Server database using the bcp utility.
    Additionally, the package allows SQL queries stored in separate files to be easily loaded, referenced and parameterized.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
Imports:
    RODBC,
    stringr,
    gdata,
    utils
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
